    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Could you explain the use-cases where this is better than:\n\n``` html\n<div id=\"sidebar\">\n  <div id=\"brands\"></div>\n  <div id=\"price\"></div>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` javascript\ninstantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\n  container: '#brands',\n  facetName: 'brands',\n  operator: 'and'\n});\ninstantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\n  container: '#price',\n  facetName: 'price',\n  operator: 'or'\n});\n```\n\nI remember this had to do with the Magento/WP implementation, but I don't remember why. \n",
