    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Facet in integration are implemented in a generic way. So right now the dom `<div id=\"brands\"></div>` and `<div id=\"price\"></div>` need to be generated because we do not know the name and number of facet in advance. This will avoid that\n",
